Chartering Manager (Tankers) - Singapore
Chartering Manager (Tankers) - Singapore
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  SGD100000 - SGD300000 per annumChartering Manager - Tankers - Singapore - Negotiable Package
A globally recognised and well respected trading house is seeking to bring in their new Chartering manager to be responsible for their DPP cargo transportation.
The successful candidate will be responsible for the groups chartering strategy, vessel optimisation, recommendation of project opportunities, developing new business opportunities and maintaining key business relationships.
The company are looking for a vastly experienced tanker charterer who has experience working in an multi-national shipping or trading company. Bi-Lingual proficiency in English and Mandarin is preferred as the client will be dealing many Mandarin speaking clients.
The company offer a negotiable salary and incentive scheme depending on experience and market relevance. Additionally this role offers an excellent career path in a multi-national environment.
For more information or to apply to this role please email tom@navis-consulting.com or call +442392 314 687.
Think Maritime - Think Navis Consulting.
